### 1. Register a new user
# send this request first to create a new user account. You can change the email and password if you want.

POST http://localhost:3000/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "username": "testuser"
}

### 2. Login with the new user

# after successful login, copy "access_token" tá»« response and use for the next requests.
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### 3. Test Get Videos 
